Sir Ian Botham was tempted to bet on Jimmy Anderson breaking his Test wickets record . 
  Anderson took one wicket on day three of the first Test in Antigua . 
  Botham is still one short of the record of 383 set by Sir Clive Lloyd . 
  Moeen Ali has been called up to the England squad for the remaining Tests . 
  Jermaine Blackwood hit his first Test century for the West Indies . 
 